snippet.title: Do Unto Others Trailer
snippet.description:
https://itch.io/jam/gmtk-2018/rate/299723
Play and rate now while the game jam rating period is up! 
Do Unto Others is a game I created from scratch in 48 hours with Sean Rugg. It's a fighting game with a twist: Every action you take towards one player ends up affecting the other player instead. Think outside the box, it's a reverse psychology party brawler!
